# {{ project_name }} Setup Guide

## Prerequisites

- Python {{ python_version }}+ (managed via UV)
- Node.js {{ node_version }}+ with pnpm
- [Task](https://taskfile.dev) (task runner)
- {{ container_runtime | title }} (container engine)

## Quick Start

```bash
# Clone and enter project
git clone <repository-url>
cd {{ project_slug }}

# Bootstrap everything
task setup

# Start all services
task up

# Run tests
task test
```

## Backend Setup

```bash
uv sync --all-groups
uv run pytest
```

## Frontend Setup

```bash
cd frontend
pnpm install
pnpm run dev
```

## Environment Variables

Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and configure:

```bash
cp .env.example .env
```

Key variables are documented in `docs/CONFIG.md`.
